CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 24, 1963, pg. 1, reads: "Nobles Dazzling City With Colorful Display - Pyramid Band - Philadelphia's Pyramid Temple Oriental Band (shown above) won second place in Music Festival. Winston O. Williams is the director.  The Music Festival was held at the Pitt Field House. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Members of Pyramid Temple No. 1 Band of Philadelphia, posed in gymnasium
